  • Method Details

    • parseFileToQuestions

      List<Question> parseFileToQuestions(org.springframework.web.multipart.MultipartFile file)
      Parses the provided CSV file into a list of Question entities.

      The CSV file is expected to have a header row and use commas as column separators. Each row is mapped to a QuestionCSV object, which is converted to a Question entity using QuestionMapper.

      Parameters:
      file - the CSV file containing questions data
      Returns:
      a list of Question entities

    • saveAll

      void saveAll(List<Question> questions)
      Saves provided list of Question entities to the database.
      Parameters:
      questions - the list of questions to save
